## File Verification

After running experiments or making changes, verify files actually updated:

**PowerShell:**
```powershell
Get-ChildItem -Path evaluation_results/ | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object Name, LastWriteTime
```

This shows you the most recent files and their timestamps, confirming that your run actually saved results.

